\end{align*}
$$
We can use this to expand a polynomial, e.g. $x^2$:
$$
Q_3^2 \begin{bmatrix}
x_1^2 \\
x_2^2 \\
x_3^2 
\end{bmatrix} = {\sqrt{œÄ} \over 3} 
\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 & 1 \\
