In other words:
$$
x^2 = {\sqrt œÄ \over 2} q_0(x) + {\sqrt œÄ \over 2\sqrt 2} q_2(x) = {1 \over 2} T_0(x) + {1 \over 2} T_2(x)
$$
which can be easily confirmed.

